      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes standard benchmark verification cases (lid-driven cavity, Poiseuille flow) demonstrating correct implementation of governing equations.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against published benchmark problems. Vendor verification reports confirm second-order spatial accuracy for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver used in this study. Gradation 1 requirement met."
