      "rationale": "MRL 2 Gradation 1 requires documentation of model inputs but not formal uncertainty quantification. Fluid properties sourced from FDA benchmark protocol. Hemolysis model constants from Giersiepen et al. (1990) as reported in peer-reviewed literature. Nominal values applied. Not formally assessed per MRL 2 scoping."
